trans-unit.source: Represents a <xref href="System.Printing.PrintDriver"></xref> property (and its value) of a printing system hardware or software component.
trans-unit.target: 나타냅니다는 <xref href="System.Printing.PrintDriver"> </xref> 인쇄 시스템 하드웨어 또는 소프트웨어 구성의 속성 (및 해당 값).

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintDriverProperty"></xref> class for the specified property.
trans-unit.target: 새 인스턴스를 초기화는 <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintDriverProperty"> </xref> 지정된 된 속성에 대 한 클래스입니다.

trans-unit.source: The `attributeName` should be spelled exactly the same as the name of some particular <xref:System.Printing.PrintDriver> property of a print system object, including casing.
trans-unit.target: `attributeName` 철자를 사용 해야 몇몇 특정의 이름을 똑같이 <xref:System.Printing.PrintDriver>대/소문자를 포함 하는 인쇄 시스템 개체의 속성입니다.</xref:System.Printing.PrintDriver>

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.QueueDriver%2A> property of a <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue> object must be spelled "QueueDriver", not "PrintDriver" or "Queuedriver".
trans-unit.target: 예를 들어는 <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.QueueDriver%2A>속성은 <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue>"PrintDriver" 또는 "Queuedriver" 아닌지 "QueueDriver" 개체를 입력 해야 합니다.</xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue> </xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.QueueDriver%2A>

trans-unit.source: The name of the <xref href="System.Printing.PrintDriver"></xref> property that the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintDriverProperty"></xref> represents.
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintDriverProperty"></xref> class that has the specified value for the specified attribute.
trans-unit.target: 새 인스턴스를 초기화는 <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintDriverProperty"> </xref> 클래스에 지정된 된 특성에 대 한 지정 된 값입니다.

trans-unit.source: The `attributeName` should be spelled exactly the same as the name of some particular <xref:System.Printing.PrintDriver> property of a print system object, including casing.
trans-unit.target: `attributeName` 철자를 사용 해야 몇몇 특정의 이름을 똑같이 <xref:System.Printing.PrintDriver>대/소문자를 포함 하는 인쇄 시스템 개체의 속성입니다.</xref:System.Printing.PrintDriver>

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.QueueDriver%2A> property of a <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue> object must be spelled "QueueDriver", not "PrintDriver" or "Queuedriver".
trans-unit.target: 예를 들어는 <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.QueueDriver%2A>속성은 <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue>"PrintDriver" 또는 "Queuedriver" 아닌지 "QueueDriver" 개체를 입력 해야 합니다.</xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue> </xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.QueueDriver%2A>

trans-unit.source: The name of the <xref href="System.Printing.PrintDriver"></xref> property that the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintDriverProperty"></xref> represents.
The value of the property that the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintDriverProperty"></xref> represents.
Gets or sets the value of the property that the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintDriverProperty"></xref> represents.
An <xref:System.Object> that can be cast to a <xref href="System.Printing.PrintDriver"></xref>.
